# http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#assignmentTitle
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#assignmentTitle> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#assignmentTitle> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
