<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#assignmentTitle> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "assignment title"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#courseCode
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#courseCode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#courseCode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#courseCode> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#Course> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#courseCode> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
