<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#moduleOrder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "module order"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#moduleTitle
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#moduleTitle> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#moduleTitle> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#moduleTitle> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#Module> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#moduleTitle> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#moduleTitle> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The title of a Module within a Course." .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#moduleTitle> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "module title"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#score
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#score> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#score> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
