# http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_LinkedData
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_LinkedData> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_LinkedData> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_LinkedData> <http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#isLearningObjectiveOf> <http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#Course_SemanticWeb> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_LinkedData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Students will be able to explain and apply Linked Data principles and publish RDF data according to Semantic Web best practices." .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_LinkedData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Linked Data Principles"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_OntologyDesign
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_OntologyDesign> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_OntologyDesign> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_OntologyDesign> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Students will be able to design and implement well-structured OWL ontologies using Protégé, applying appropriate class hierarchies, properties, and restrictions." .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_OntologyDesign> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ontology Design"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_SemanticReasoning
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_SemanticReasoning> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_SemanticReasoning> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective> .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_SemanticReasoning> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Students will be able to apply semantic reasoning using OWL reasoners such as HermiT to infer implicit knowledge from ontologies." .
<http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#LearningObjective_SemanticReasoning> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Semantic Reasoning"@en .
# 
# http://www.example.org/elearning-ontology#Module_Week1
